snippet.textDisplay: Please everybody note that if someone praised Ail (peace be upon him) it doesnt make him/her a Shia or Sunni. Hazrat Ail (peace be upon him) was the cousin as well as son in law of Hazrat Muhammad (peace be upon him). He was one of the 4 greatest companions of our Prophet (peace be upon him) and also one of the greatest Khalifas of Islam. Every Muslim must love Hazrat Ali (peace be upon him) with respect. These Sufi songs most of the time praised hazrat Ali (peace be upon him) because he was the source of mystic Islamic faith which leads to Sufism.
